&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3578&quot; title=&quot;Scala DataStream API does not support Rich Window Functions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-3578&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-3578&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;streaming scala&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Support RichFunctions for Scala WindowFunction and AllWindowFunction&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This also consolidates the various wrapper classes for fold() and reduce() functions.&lt;/p&gt;

